5. FINDINGS

The Institute concludes that the primary output of the Non-Embodied Strategic Entity is confidence.

Confidence, when delivered at sufficient volume and accompanied by slide decks, becomes operationally indistinguishable from productivity in 73% of corporate environments.

We define this phenomenon as:

Performative Competence Through Vocabulary (PCTV)

Organizations exposed to PCTV for more than 6 months begin reorganizing themselves around the entity despite the entity being unable to open a door.

